    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up as a House.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your limbs stretch through endless rooms filled with grotesque creatures. You can never see outside of yourself, never feel the world that lies beyond the fleshy walls of your body. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You manage your insides as best as you can, but you wonder: are you a good house or just a pale afterthought of the House Before? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The House Before is a story-driven adventure game with light puzzles. Encounters with each new creature unfold through mini-games and short dialogues. The House Before takes around 2 hours to complete. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore your guts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779750/extras/f7245ac4add25be904c3e4a3d9e1dbf2.poster.avif?t=1767894819\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779750/extras/f7245ac4add25be904c3e4a3d9e1dbf2.webm?t=1767894819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779750/extras/f7245ac4add25be904c3e4a3d9e1dbf2.mp4?t=1767894819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heal old wounds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1779750/extras/758e2beab14116b79b6a9fa351aa3304.poster.avif?t=1767894819\" width=1170 height=6